## 7. Material Language (for CG5 3D CGI rendering)

| Surface | Poppy Playtime Specific |
|---|---|
| **Fabric/Fur** | Matted synthetic plush (Huggy/Kissy/CatNap), inside-out exposed stuffing (Giblet/Outimals), yarn (Yarnaby legacy) |
| **Plastic/Porcelain** | Cracked porcelain (Poppy's face), elastic plastic (Mommy legacy), fashion doll plastic (Lily) |
| **Metal** | Rusted factory infrastructure, GrabPack mechanical hands, endoskeletons, chains/hooks |
| **Organic** | Exposed muscle/bone under torn toy shells, biological Bigger Bodies, poppy gel (luminous liquid) |
| **Hair** | Controllable braids with embedded bones (Lily), matted fur patches (Giblet) |
| **Blood-like liquid** | Red fluid circulating in Outimal hands |

